    "longBusinessSummary": "Nam Hoa Trading and Production Corporation engages in the production and trading of school supplies and wooden toys in Vietnam. It offers kids toys, such as building blocks, traffic and food strings, jenga, cars, planes, rattle towers, baby walkers, xylophone music boxes, number towers, pathfinders, the alphabet games, stringed toys, weather blocks, and clock block and number puzzles; and household products, including cutting boards, knife rests, trays, paper holders, tissue boxes, toothpick boxes, chopsticks, pot liners, and other household products. The company also provides gifts and stationery products; and kids furniture products, such as doll prams, wooden tables and drawers, hanger stands, rocking horses, and bed trays. It exports its products to the United States, Europe, Australia, Japan, Korea, and internationally. The company was founded in 1993 and is based in Ho Chi Minh City, Vietnam.",
